This is a list of [[Sites of Special Scientific Interest]] (SSSIs) in [[Northumberland]], England.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://designatedsites.naturalengland.org.uk/SiteList.aspx?countyCode=32|title=Designated Sites View - Northumberland|publisher=Natural England|website=Natural England website|access-date=6 May 2016}}</ref>
[[English Nature]], the designating body for SSSIs in [[England]], uses the [[Metropolitan and non-metropolitan counties of England|1974-1996 county system]], and this list follows the same approach. Some sites one may expect to find here could therefore be in the [[List of Sites of Special Scientific Interest in County Durham|County Durham]] or [[List of Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Tyne and Wear|Tyne and Wear]] lists.
For other counties, see [[List of SSSIs by Area of Search]].
